sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open channel thread
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/channels/{channelId}/messages
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>DB: Check channel membership and load messages
    DB-->>API: Access data + message list
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + messages
    Frontend-->>User: Display message history
